%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20just%20showed%20the%20world%20his%20shiny%20new%20Robovan.%20There's%20already%20a%20Chinese%20vehicle%20with%20the%20same%20name.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20attending%20the%20Cannes%20Lions%20International%20Festival%20Of%20Creativity%3B%20a%20Tesla%20Robovan%20prototype%20makes%20its%20way%20through%20a%20Los%20Angeles-area%20set.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6708b9df6ac7b701e7ca51db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20unveiled%20the%20Robovan%20on%20Thursday.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Bord%2FWireImage%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETesla's%20new%20Robovan%20has%20a%20Chinese%20counterpart%20with%20the%20same%20name.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWeRide%20unveiled%20its%20Robovan%20back%20in%202021.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20separate%20robotics%20startup%2C%20Starship%20Technologies%2C%20filed%20a%20US%20trademark%20application%20for%20%26quot%3BRobovan%26quot%3B%20in%202017.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-about-teslas-new-robovan-so-far-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobovan%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%3C%2Fa%3E%20novel%20surprise%20at%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20Robot%26quot%3B%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20something%20about%20it%20wasn't%20as%20novel%20%E2%80%94%20its%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeRide%2C%20a%20Chinese%20autonomous%20driving%20startup%2C%20unveiled%20its%20own%20self-driving%20cargo%20van%20in%202021.%20WeRide%20named%20its%20product%20the%20Robovan%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20CEO%2C%20Tony%20Han%2C%20touted%20it%20as%20being%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20a%20passenger%20and%20logistics%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20autonomous%20driving%20vehicle.%20If%20you%20put%20a%20seat%20there%20it%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20robotaxi%20car.%20If%20you%20put%20a%20cabinet%20there%20it%20is%20really%20a%20logistics%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20told%20CNBC%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20we%20do%20both%3F%26quot%3B%20Han%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeRide%20said%20it%20is%20partnering%20with%20JMC-Ford%20Motors%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20state-owned%20automaker%20Jiangling%20Motors%20Corp%20and%20Ford%2C%20to%20manufacture%20the%20Robovan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20WeRide%20said%20it%20obtained%20a%20license%20to%20conduct%20road%20tests%20for%20the%20vehicle%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%20China.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20WeRide%20said%20it%20had%20received%20%26quot%3Bover%2010%2C000%20indication%20orders%20from%20a%20leading%20express%20delivery%20company%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20WeRide%20wasn't%20the%20first%20company%20interested%20in%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BRobovan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202017%2C%20a%20company%20called%20Starship%20Technologies%20filed%20a%20trademark%20for%20%26quot%3BRobovan%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20United%20States%20Patent%20and%20Trademark%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarship%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20autonomous%20delivery%20robots%2C%20was%20founded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskype-engineer-warns-ai-weapons-race-people-stay-inside-drones-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESkype%3C%2Fa%3E%20cofounders%20Ahti%20Heinla%20and%20Janus%20Friis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.starship.xyz%2Fpress_releases%2Frobovan-by-starship-technologies-and-mercedes-benz-vans-future-proof-local-delivery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%202016%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20work%20with%20Mercedes-Benz%20to%20develop%20a%20%26quot%3BRobovan%26quot%3B%20for%