ias-semi-final-chances%2Farticleshow%2F114140017.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20chances%20of%20reaching%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semi-finals%20depend%20on%20the%20outcomes%20of%20other%20Group%20A%20matches.%20With%20both%20India%20and%20Australia%20tied%20on%20points%2C%20India%20must%20defeat%20Australia%20in%20their%20final%20match%20to%20remain%20in%20contention.%20Key%20scenarios%20involve%20Australia's%20performance%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20which%20will%20impact%20the%20race%20for%20the%20top%20two%20spots%2C%20making%20every%20game%20critical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22HIJAM%20RAJU%20SINGH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-womens-t20-world-cup%2Fwomens-t20-world-cup-how-australia-vs-pakistan-will-impact-indias-semi-final-chances%2Farticleshow%2F114140017.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahadev%20Betting%20App%20Accused%20May%20Be%20Extradited%20From%20Dubai%20Soon%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%20Chandrakar%20-%20a%20primary%20accused%20in%20the%20Rs%205%2C000-crore%20Mahdev%20app%20betting%20case%20-%20will%20be%20extradited%20from%20the%20UAE%20and%20brought%20to%20India%20within%20a%20week%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extradition%20process%20-%20greenlit%20by%20UAE%20authorities%20after%20the%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20intervened%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20probe%20agency%20-%20is%20in%20the%20final%20stages%2C%20sources%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakar%20-%20who%20operated%20a%20juice%20shop%20in%20Chhattisgarh's%20Bhilai%20before%20rising%20to%20head%20an%20alleged%20international%20betting%20syndicate%20-%20has%20been%20in%20police%20custody%20in%20the%20UAE%20since%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20detained%20in%20Dubai%20-%20and%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20-%20based%20on%20an%20Interpol%20Red%20Corner%20Notice.%20His%20associate%20Ravi%20Uppal%20had%20been%20detained%2C%20also%20in%20Dubai%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ED%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20ran%20the%20Mahadev%20network%20-%20which%20allegedly%20included%20a%20nexus%20of%20police%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20and%20politicians%20to%20shield%20the%20illegal%20activities%20-%20from%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECall%20centres%20were%20opened%20across%20Malaysia%2C%20Thailand%2C%20and%20India%2C%20and%20also%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20through%20which%20illegal%20betting%20was%20conducted%20by%20creating%20an%20entire%20ecosystem%20of%20interlinked%20mobile%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20claimed%20the%20network%20consisted%20of%20around%204%2C000%20'panel%20operators'%2C%20based%20across%20different%20states%20in%20India%2C%20with%20handling%20around%20200%20customers%20placing%20bets.%20Using%20this%20method%2C%20the%20two%20made%20at%20least%20Rs%20200%20crore%20daily%2C%20and%20managed%20to%20build%20a%20criminal%20empire%20in%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20September%20last%20year%20the%20ED%20seized%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20417%20crore%20from%20raids%20in%2039%20locations%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20and%20Bhopal%3B%20the%20network's%20India%20operation%20was%20run%20with%20help%20from%20two%20other%20associates%20of%20Chandrakar%20-%20Anil%20and%20Sunil%20Dammani.%20The%20former%20was%20also%20tasked%20with%20paying%20off%20cops%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20and%20politicians%20with%20the%20illegally%20acquired%20money%20to%20buy%20their%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20'protectors'%20named%20by%20the%20ED%20is%20Chandra%20Bhushan%20Verma%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20member%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%20department%2C%20who%20was%20paid%20via%20money%20routed%20from%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20was%20passed%20through%20a%20jeweller%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20of%20Raipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%20Anil%20Dammani%20said%20his%20brother%20and%20he%2C%20over%20the%20previous%2024-36%20months%2C%20passed%20nearly%20Rs%2065%20crore%20in%20illegal%20money%20through%20their%20hawala%20network.%20His%20cut%20was%20Rs%206%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20emerged%20that%20the%20police%20officer%2C%20Verma%2C%20had%20direct%20links%20with%20the%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel's%20political%20advisor%2C%20Vinod%20Verma%2C%20which%20helped%20keep%20a%20tab%20on%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20led%20to%20the%20Congress%20leader%20becoming%20mired%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%3B%20this%20was%20after%20a%20man%20claiming%20to%20be%20the%20'real%20owner'%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20app%20alleged%20he%20gave%20Mr%20Baghel%20Rs%20508%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20claimed%20a%20link%20between%20the%20man%20-%20Shubham%20Soni%20-%20and%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20after%20it%20seized%20Rs%205.39%20crore%2C%20in%20cash%2C%20from%20a%20hawala%20courier%20called%20Asim%20Das.%20In%20March%20-%20weeks%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20-%20Chhattisgarh%20Police%20filed%20a%20FIR%20against%20Mr%20Baghel%20and%2018%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baghel%20denied%20all%20charges%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20FIR%20is%20politically%20motivated%2C%20I%20was%20deliberately%20implicated%20under%20pressure.%20It%20was%20done%20due%20to%20political%20vendetta.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20claimed%20ED%20action%20against%20him%20was%20on%20instructions%20from%20the%20BJP%3B%20the%20ED%20reports%20to%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20the%20Congress%20government%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20identified%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20as%20the%20betting%20syndicate%20bosses%20and%20issued%20a%20notice%2C%20and%20that%20since%20they%20were%20not%20in%20state%20jurisdiction%2C%20it%20was%20the%20central%20government's%20responsibility%20to%20track%20down%20and%20apprehend%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chandrakar%20and%20Uppal%20(and%20Mahadev%20app)%20story%20reportedly%20began%20with%20the%20two%20becoming%20addicted%20to%20online%20gambling.%20This%20prompted%20the%20two%20to%20gather%20their%20savings%20for%20a%20gambling%20spree%20in%20Dubai.%20Once%20there%20they%20met%20a%20sheikh%20and%20a%20Pakistani%20national%2C%20and%20hatched%20this%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESourabh%20Chandrakar%20also%20reportedly%20roped%20his%20brother%2C%20Satish%2C%20into%20the%20crime%2C%20putting%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20running%20four%20call%20centres%20and%20giving%20him%20a%20five%20per%20cent%20stake.%20Satish%20also%20had%20links%20to%20Tapan%20Sarkar%20-%20a%20noted%20gangster%20and%20drug%20mafia%20boss%20who%20is%20now%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20dragnet%20has%20also%20hauled%20in%20Bollywood%20celebrities%2C%20among%20the%20most%20notable%20of%20whom%20is%20actor%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%2C%20who%20was%20accused%20of%20promoting%20a%20subsidiary%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor%20Sahil%20Khan%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case.%20He%20got%20bail%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728628980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F65fppjuo_saurabh-chandrakar_625x300_27_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-accused-sourabh-chandrakar-ravi-uppal-may-be-extradited-from-dubai-soon-sources-6765315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sourabh%20Chandrakar%20-%20a%20primary%20accused%20in%20the%20Rs%205%2C000-crore%20Mahdev%20app%20betting%20case%20-%20will%20be%20extradited%20from%20the%20UAE%20and%20brought%20to%20India%20within%20a%20week%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20Friday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-betting-app-accused-sourabh-chandrakar-ravi-uppal-may-be-extradited-from-dubai-soon-sources-6765315%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampU