in%20south%20Lebanon.%20It%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20since%20fighting%20escalated%20between%20the%20IDF%20and%20the%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20on%20September%2023.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20UN%20mission%20confirmed%20two%20peacekeepers%20were%20injured%20after%20an%20IDF%20Merkava%20tank%20fired%20a%20shell%20towards%20an%20observation%20tower%20at%20the%20UNIFIL%20headquarters%20in%20south%20Lebanon's%20Naqura%2C%20directly%20hitting%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20peacekeepers%20did%20not%20suffer%20serious%20injuries%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20they%20remain%20in%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20They%20are%20Indonesian%20nationals%2C%20a%20UNIFIL%20spokesperson%20said.%20Indonesia%20is%20also%20a%20major%20contributor%20of%20troops%20to%20the%20UNIFIL.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIndonesia's%20UN%20ambassador%20Hari%20Prabowo%20said%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20demonstrates%20how%20Israel%20positioned%20itself%20above%20international%20law%2C%20above%20impunity%20and%20above%20our%20shared%20values%20of%20peace.%26quot%3B%C2%A0Israel%20claimed%20its%20military%20%26quot%3Bopened%20fire%20in%20the%20area%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20UNIFIL%20base%20after%20telling%20UN%20forces%20to%20seek%20shelter.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20tower%20in%20Nakura%2C%20two%20personnel%20were%20injured%2C%20and%20they%20were%20from%20Indonesia%2C%26quot%3B%20Indonesia%20Foreign%20Minister%20Retno%20Marsudi%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20She%20added%20the%20two%20peacekeepers%20had%20sustained%20light%20injuries%20and%20are%20in%20hospital%20for%20further%20observation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EItaly's%20Defence%20Minister%20Guido%20Crosetto%20said%20the%20attack%20and%20other%20incidents%20that%20the%20UNIFIL%20blames%20on%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bcould%20constitute%20war%20crimes%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20asked%20for%20an%20explanation%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20not%20a%20mistake%26quot%3B.%20The%20Defence%20Minister%20descr