cap-250-index-funds-details-here-124101100291_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gautam%20Adani%20On%20How%20Ratan%20Tata%20Shaped%20His%20Business%20Decisions%2C%20Philosophy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20has%20called%20Ratan%20Tata%20%26quot%3Bthe%20perfect%20Renaissance%20man%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20obituary%20remembering%20one%20of%20the%20most%20brilliant%20entrepreneurs%20of%20his%20generation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20describe%20him%20merely%20as%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20industrialists%20of%20our%20time%20is%20a%20gross%20understatement.%20Ratan%20Tata%20was%20a%20remarkable%20individual%2C%20possessing%20extraordinary%20capabilities%20that%20transcended%20traditional%20business%20boundaries.%20There%20is%20hardly%20any%20field%20where%20he%20has%20not%20left%20his%20mark%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2Cnoindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fratan-tata-the-perfect-renaissance-man%2Farticleshow%2F114129126.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ewrote%20in%20The%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20no%20surprise%20that%20his%20journey%20and%20body%20of%20work%20have%20inspired%20legions%20of%20generational%20entrepreneurs%2C%20both%20in%20India%20and%20abroad.%20I%20am%20just%20one%20of%20the%20countless%20individuals%20who%20have%20benefited%20immensely%20from%20his%20influence.%20While%20an%20anatomy%20of%20his%20legacy%20will%20occupy%20thousands%20of%20pages%2C%20I%20am%20briefly%20sharing%20three%20major%20areas%20where%20he%20shaped%20my%20business%20decisions%20and%20philosophy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20wrote%20of%20the%20Chairman%20Emeritus%20of%20Tata%20Sons%20and%20a%20philanthropist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERatan%20Tata%20died%20at%2086%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20he%20would%20undergo%20routine%20medical%20investigations%20due%20to%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20wrote%20that%20the%20international%20ventures%20of%20his%20Group%20were%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20Ratan%20Tata%20-%20one%20of%20the%20first%20to%20truly%20believe%20in%20India%20and%20the%20potential%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20Among%20his%20many%20legacies%2C%20one%20that%20stands%20out%20for%20me%20is%20how%20he%20took%20Tata%20and%20corporate%20India%20global.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20first%20to%20let%20the%20world%20know%20that%20India%20stands%20tall%20and%20can%20compete%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20He%20carried%20the%20Indian%20flag%20across%20shores%2C%20not%20only%20to%20build%20a%20bigger%20company%20but%20to%20establish%20an%20Indian%20imprint%2C%20rooted%20in%20our%20heritage%2C%20culture%20and%20pride.%20His%20international%20forays%20through%20Tetley%2C%20Corus%20and%20Jaguar%20Land%20Rover%20were%20inspirations%20for%20me%2C%20when%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20comforts%20of%20our%20own%20country%20into%20Australia%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Israel%20and%20now%20Africa%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqn7aukf8_ratan-tata_625x300_10_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%40ratantata%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly%2C%20the%20development%20of%20our%20greenfield%20Navi%20Mumbai%20International%20Airport%20had%20multiple%20challenges%20and%20was%20a%20Sisyphean%20project.%20While%20I%20was%20evaluating%20it%2C%20in%20that%20crucial%20moment%2C%20it%20was%20Ratan%20Tata's%20words%20of%20encouragement%20which%20moved%20the%20needle%20for%20me.%20Now%20as%20this%20airport%20is%20soon%20going%20to%20become%20reality%2C%20he%20will%20be%20greatly%20missed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLastly%2C%20for%20him%2C%20success%20was%20nev