M%20Sheikh%20Hasina%2C%20a%20move%20that%20might%20clear%20the%20decks%20for%20a%20farewell%20Test%20match%20at%20home%20against%20South%20Africa.%20He%20is%20targetting%20the%20opening%20Test%20starting%20October%2021%20in%20Mirpur%20as%20his%20swansong.%20There%20is%20a%20second%20Test%20in%20Chittagong%20but%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20Shakib%20will%20play%20the%20first%20game%20and%20then%20fly%20off%20to%20the%20USA%2C%20where%20he%20is%20settled%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirstly%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20pay%20my%20respects%20to%20all%20the%20students%20who%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%2C%20led%20the%20anti-discrimination%20movement%2C%20and%20were%20martyred%20or%20injured%20during%20the%20people's%20uprising%2C%26quot%3B%20Shakib%2C%20who%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20a%20murder%20case%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20wrote%20on%20his%20official%20Facebook%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20no%20sacrifice%20can%20compensate%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20loved%20one%2C%20nothing%20can%20fill%20the%20void%20of%20losing%20a%20child%20or%20a%20brother%2C%20to%20those%20of%20you%20who%20were%20hurt%20by%20my%20silence%20during%20this%20critical%20period%2C%20I%20respect%20your%20feelings%20and%20sincerely%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20in%20your%20place%2C%20I%20too%20might%20have%20been%20upset%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20all-rounder%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20in%20the%20Hasina%20government%20that%20was%20overthrown%20owing%20to%20a%20student%20protest%20against%20quota%20in%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20recent%20Test%20series%20in%20India%2C%20the%2037-year-old%2C%20who%20has%20played%2071%20Tests%20for%20Bangladesh%2C%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20play%20his%20final%20five-day%20game%20at%20home%20provided%20the%20current%20regime%20can%20arrange%20a%20security%20cover%20for%20him.%20He%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20UAE%20after%20the%20Tests%20against%20India%2C%20having%20already%20bid%20adieu%20to%20the%20T20Is%20following%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20student%20during%20the%20unrest%20but%20Shakib%20was%20playing%20a%20T20%20league%20in%20Canada%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20Cricket%20Board's%20new%20president%20Faruque%20Ahmed%20had%20dismissed%20Shakib's%20request%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20BCB%20was%20not%20a%20security%20agency%20and%20could%20not%20guarantee%20any%20cover%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20sports%20advisor%20to%20the%20government%20Asif%20Mahmud%20said%20that%20he%20could%20be%20provided%20security%20provided%20he%20made%20his%20political%20stance%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20star%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20his%20only%20target%20as%20a%20politician%20was%20development%20of%20his%20hometown%20Magura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20briefly%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20the%20Magura-1%20constituency.%20My%20political%20involvement%20was%20primarily%20driven%20by%20my%20desire%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20development%20of%20my%20hometown%20Magura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20know%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20directly%20impact%20the%20development%20of%20one's%20area%20without%20a%20specific%20role%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20wish%20to%20develop%20this%20area%20is%20what%20motivated%20me%20to%20become%20an%20MP.%20However%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20my%20primary%20identity%20is%20as%20a%20cricketer%20for%20Bangladesh.%20No%20matter%20where%20I%20have%20been%20or%20in%20what%20position%2C%20I%20have%20always%20carried%20cricket%20in%20my%20heart.%26quot%3B%20Shakib's%20public%20apology%20is%20likely%20ensure%20that%20he%20gets%20a%20farewell%20in%20Bangladesh%20Whites%20at%20his%20favourite