nsider.com%2Ftesla%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Robotaxi%20at%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20Robot%26quot%3B%20event%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20autonomous%20vehicle%2C%20which%20has%20faced%20delays%2C%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Musk's%20vision%20for%20a%20Tesla%20ride-hailing%20network.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bvalue%20of%20Tesla%20overwhelmingly%20is%20autonomy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20long-awaited%20Robotaxi%20has%20finally%20been%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20off%20Tesla's%20upcoming%20driverless%20taxi%20at%20its%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20Robot%26quot%3B%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unveiling%20took%20place%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-robotaxi-event-warner-bros-discovery-studio-report-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarner%20Bros.%20Discovery's%20movie%20studio%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Burbank%2C%20California%2C%20which%20features%20a%20suburban%20lot.%20The%20location%20allowed%20Tesla%20to%20show%20off%20its%20autonomous%20driving%20capabilities%20without%20running%20into%20any%20unexpected%20situations%20with%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20walked%20into%20the%20event%20and%20entered%20a%20sleek-looking%20silver%20Robotaxi%2C%20a%20two-door%20vehicle%C2%A0that%20opened%20upward%20with%20butterfly-style%20doors.%20The%20Robotaxi%2C%20also%20referred%20to%20as%20Cybercab%2C%20then%20took%20Musk%20on%20a%20ride%20around%20the%20lot%20before%20he%20exited%20and%20took%20the%20stage%20to%20kick%20off%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20the%20Robotaxi%20has%20no%20steering%20wheel%20or%20pedals%2C%20and%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20plugged%20in.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%20the%20electric%20veh