Tesla%20has%20been%20scrutinized%20in%20the%20past%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-autopilot-safety-assisted-self-driving-systems-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafety%20of%20its%20driver-assistance%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20also%20announced%20the%20Robovan%2C%20a%20large%20shuttle%20van%20that%20Musk%20said%20could%20seat%20up%20to%2020%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tesla%20Robovan%20prototype%20makes%20its%20way%20through%20a%20Los%20Angeles-area%20set.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6708978e3f2165d716e0167c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22834%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Tesla%20Robovan%20prototype%20makes%20its%20way%20through%20a%20Los%20Angeles-area%20set%3Cp%3EScreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20also%20touted%20Optimus%2C%20a%20humanoid%20robot%20that%20he%20said%20would%20cost%20%2428%2C000%20to%20%2430%2C000%2C%20but%20did%20not%20share%20a%20timeline%20on%20when%20the%20robot%20would%20be%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20will%20be%20the%20biggest%20product%20ever%2C%20of%20any%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20everyone's%20going%20to%20want%20their%20Optimus%20buddy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20presentation%2C%20several%20of%20the%20robots%20danced%20on%20the%20stage%20to%20a%20light%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221482%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Optimus%20robot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670897e86ac7b701e7ca507c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221376%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20Optimus%20robot%20prototypes%20walk%20onto%20the%20stage%20with%20Elon%20Musk%3Cp%3EScreengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20ahead%20of%20the%20reveal%2C%20Mu