2Fa%3E%20was%20still%20open%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20get%20out%20of%20there%2C%20and%20it%20was%20scary%20not%20knowing%20how%20the%20weather%20was%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20ride%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20parks%20worker%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20four%20employees%20who%20work%20in%20the%20various%20parks%20at%20Disney%20World.%20They%20expressed%20their%20disappointment%20with%20how%20the%20company%20managed%20scheduling%2C%20logistics%2C%20and%20safety%20precautions%20in%20the%20hours%20leading%20up%20to%20Hurricane%20Milton's%20arrival%2C%20from%20refusing%20to%20cancel%20work%20as%20weather%20conditions%20worsened%20to%20engaging%20in%20what%20sources%20described%20as%20infrequent%20communication%20that%20left%20employees%20feeling%20like%20they%20were%20flying%20blind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20called%20%26quot%3Bcast%20members%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20requested%20their%20names%20and%20roles%20remain%20anonymous%2C%20citing%20fears%20of%20possible%20reprisals%20from%20Disney.%20Their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShutdowns%20are%20costly%3A%20Before%20the%20storm%2C%20Goldman%20Sachs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F10%2F08%2Fhurrican-milton-could-hit-disney-earnings-goldman-says.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20hurricane%20could%20cost%20Disney's%20lucrative%20parks%20division%20up%20to%20%24200%20million.%20The%20company%20also%20had%20to%20balance%20workers'%20well-being%20with%20serving%20eager%20guests%20who%20pay%20thousands%20for%20what%20can%20be%20once-in-a-lifetime%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6b03adc-69cb-4a58-a687-f9f4dccee998%5C%22%3EWorkers%20stayed%20well%20into%20the%20afternoon%20to%20close%20things%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20closed%20its%20four%20parks%20early%20on%20Wednesday%20due%20to%20the%20storm.%20Hollywood%20Studios%20and%20Animal%20Kingdom%20closed%20at%201%20p.m.%20for%20guests%2C%20and%20Magic%20Kingdom%20and%20Epcot%20closed%20at%202%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20closing%2C%20though%2C%20the%20parks%20started%20to%20feel%20like%20wet%20and%20rainy%20ghost%20towns%2C%20cast%20members%20told%20BI.%20Attendance%20at%20Magic%20Kingdom%2C%20the%20park%20best%20known%20for%20its%20storybook%20castle%2C%20dwindled%20to%20roughly%2010%25%2C%20the%20first%20employee%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wish%20the%20park%20wouldn't%20have%20opened%20up%20for%20the%20day%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20employee%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20workers%20told%20BI%20that%20staff%20were%20expected%20to%20stay%20on%20hand%20through%20and%20after%20closing%20to%20help%20batten%20down%20the%20hatches%2C%20which%20left%20some%20feeling%20unsettled%20and%20unsafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20around%202%3A45%20p.m.%2C%20when%20one%20of%20the%20workers%20said%20they%20left%2C%20Orange%20County%2C%20where%20Disney%20World%20is%20located%2C%20was%20already%20under%20a%20state%20of%20emergency%20and%20a%20tornado%20warning.%20Officials%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNWSMelbourne%2Fstatus%2F1843954883596337170%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%20could%20face%20danger%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20flooding%2C%20and%20the%20forecast%20warned%20of%20tropical%20storm%20force%20winds%20reaching%2045%20to%2065%20mph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20those%20who%20spoke%20with%20BI%2C%20people%20who%20identified%20themselves%20as%20Disney%20parks%20workers%20took%20to%20social%20media%2C%20posting%20on%20TikTok%20and%20X%2C%20voicing%20similar%20complaints%20and%20sharing%20what%20it%20was%20like%20working%20in%20a%20mostly-empty%20amusement%20park%20as%20the%20tempest%20closed%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20prioritizes%20the%20well-being%20of%20those%20on%20park%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSafety%20is%20always%20our%20first%20and%20most%20important%20factor%20when%20making%20decisions%20that%20will%20affect%20our%20cast%20members%20and%20guests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20throughout%20the%20storm%2C%20we%20provided%20frequent%20and%20timely%20updates%20on%20our%20changes%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20returned%20home%20hours%20before%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20weather%20reached%20Central%20Florida.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225cf50e41-04dc-4be2-89d4-9c5935137c1c%5C%22%3EWorkers%20faced%20a%20dilemma%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20look%20after%20stranded%20guests%2C%20Disney%20runs%20a%20special%20%26quot%3Bride-out%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20where%20staffers%20collect%20slightly%20extra%20pay%20than%20the%20norm%20by%20volunteering%20to%20work%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-weathered-hurricane-milton-at-disney-hotel-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20duty%20during%20a%20storm.%20The%20Disney%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20roughly%205%2C000%20cast%20members%20in%20Florida%20volunteered%20to%20work%20ride-out%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20parks%20workers%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20pointed%20out%20that%20ride-out%20shifts%20happen%20when%20workers%20put%20their%20hands%20up%20to%20complete%20them%2C%20and%20come%20with%20a%20room%20where%20employees%20can%20sleep%20during%20a%20storm.%20That's%20different%20from%20the%20shifts%20that%20cast%20members%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20cash-strapped%20employees%20felt%20like%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20skipping%20out%20on%20a%20chunk%20of%20their%20pay%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Disney%20World%2C%20workers'%20minimum%20wage%20starts%20at%20%2418%20an%20hour.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20some%20employees%20faced%20a%20dilemma%3A%20Work%20until%20their%20managers%20told%20them%20their%20shift%20was%20done%2C%20even%20if%20it%20meant%20staying%20in%20the%20face%20of%20dire%20weather%20forecasts%2C%20or%20leave%20early%20but%20accept%20fractional%20pay%20only%20for%20the%20hours%20they%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20like%2C%20'We%20need%20our%20money.%20We%20want%20our%20money%2C'%26quot%3B%20recalled%20the%20first%20parks%20worker%2C%20who%20completed%20a%20full%20shift%20and%20only%20learned%20about%20the%20pay%20reductions%20by%20reading%20an%20explanation%20of%20the%20policy%20that%20someone%20had%20scrawled%20on%20a%20board%20backstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20stayed%20a%20full%20shift%20said%20they%20wished%20they'd%20had%20more%20time%20to%20get%20gas%20and%20groceries%20before%20the%20storm%20came%20ashore.%20The%20Disney%20spokesperson%20said%20gas%20stations%20were%20open%20on%20the%20property%20specifically%20for%20cast%20members%2C%20but%20three%20of%20the%20parks%20employees%20who%20spoke%20to%20BI%20said%20they%20hadn't%20heard%20of%20such%20a%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20I%20know%20knew%20anything%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20second%20employee%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20tried%20to%20get%20gas%20on%20property%20on%20Tuesday%20and%20was%20unable%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20since%20the%20pump%20was%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20also%20closed%20several%20hotels%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Fort%20Wilderness%20Resort%20%26amp%3B%20Campground%2C%20the%20Copper%20Creek%20Cabins%20at%20Disney's%20Wilderness%20Lodge%2C%20and%20the%20Treehouse%20Villas%20at%20the%20Saratoga%20Springs%20Resort%20%26amp%3B%20Spa%20%E2%80%94%20at%2011%20a.m.%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20employee%20at%20one%20of%20those%20properties%20said%20some%20managers%20instructed%20staffers%20to%20stay%20for%20another%20four%20hours%2C%20until%203%20p.m%2C.%20to%20complete%20a%20full%20shift%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%2C%20by%20midday%2C%20the%20rain%20was%20coming%20down%20hard%2C%20and%20there%20was%20almost%20nothing%20to%20do%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e368bfd5-1de6-4a93-9fc2-94335f1fedc3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBack%20to%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Disney's%20parks%20remained%20closed%20to%20guests%20Thursday%2C%20BI%20viewed%20a%20screenshot%20of%20an%20internal%20communication%20showing%20that%20the%20company%20expected%20some%20workers%20to%20participate%20in%20Thursday's%20clean-up%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20storm%2C%20we%20may%20need%20Cast%20to%20help%20with%20post-storm%20recovery%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20message%2C%20which%20was%20posted%20on%20Cast%20Life%2C%20an%20app%20Disney%20uses%20to%20share%20mass%20updates%20with%20staffers.%20%26quot%3BCast%20scheduled%20to%20work%20on%20Oct.%2010%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20areas%20that%20will%20not%20be%20opening%20to%20Guests%20%E2%80%94%20should%20continue%20to%20call%20local%20area%20Cast%20Hotlines%20and%20check%20their%20schedule%20on%20Disney%20Cast%20Life%20Web%20%2F%20App%20for%20information%20regarding%20their%20schedule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20they%20not%20only%20expect%20me%20to%20call%20but%20potentially%20go%20out%20in%20the%20parks%20to%20clean%20up%20is%20crazy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20Disney%20employee%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20sickening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20this%20person%20elected%20not%20to%20go%20in%20on%20Thursday%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20they%20would%20face%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20feel%20safe%20driving%20at%207%20a.m.%20tomorrow%20when%20this%20is%20all%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20evening.%20%26quot%3BOrlando%20is%20just%20unique%20because%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20are%20inland%2C%20but%20we%20see%20scary%20rain%20and%20terrifying%20winds.%20And%20just%20because%20we%20aren't%20washed%20away%20and%20dealing%20with%20storm%20surge%20and%20structural%20damage%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20isn't%20scary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20they%20could%20call%20the%20Disney%20coordinators%20to%20request%20an%20excuse%20from%20work%2C%20sources%20said%20it%20wasn't%20that%20simple.%20Employees%20with%20unexcused%20absences%20have%20historically%20been%20slapped%20with%20%26quot%3Bpoints%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20demerits%20on%20their%20records%2C%20they%20noted.%20A%20proliferation%20of%20points%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20reprimand%20and%2C%20ultimately%2C%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20house%20could%20be%20underwater%2C%20and%20they%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20call%20out%20and%20take%20the%20point%2C'%26quot%3B%20the%20second%20Disney%20employee%20said%2C%20recalling%20past%20hurricanes%20when%20cast%20members%20stressed%20about%20how%20they'd%20get%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%2080%2C000%20staffers%2C%20the%20Disney%20World%20Resort%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20single-site%20employers%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20It's%20the%20crown%20jewel%20of%20the%20Disney%20empire%2C%20which%20generated%20%245.8%20billion%20across%20its%20domestic%20parks%20and%20cruises%20in%20the%20three%20months%20ending%20June%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Disney%20employee%20with%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter.%20Reed%20Alexander%20can%20be%20reached%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aralexander%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eralexander%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20or%20SMS%2Fthe%20encrypted%20app%20Signal%20at%20(561)%20247-5758.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-employees-felt-unsafe-working-hours-before-hurricane-milton-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728608033000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670876873f2165d716e0152a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F