%3EThat's%20when%20Cusick%20and%20his%20friend%20noticed%20what%20looked%20almost%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Blump%20of%20mud%26quot%3B%20sitting%20underneath%20an%20overpass%2C%20anywhere%20from%2050%20to%20150%20feet%20away%20from%20where%20the%20Rivian%20was%20originally%20parked.%20Silt%20and%20mud%20from%20the%20Swannanoa%20River%2C%20Cusick%20said%2C%20had%20engulfed%20his%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERelief%20briefly%20washed%20over%20Cusick%2C%20but%20he%20immediately%20assumed%20his%20car%20was%20totaled%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20way%20in%20hell%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20into%20this%20thing%20and%20boot%20it%20right%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Cusick%20walked%20up%20to%20the%20Rivian%2C%20the%20door%20handle%2C%20which%20sits%20flush%20into%20the%20door%20panel%20much%20like%20Tesla's%2C%20popped%20out.%20Inside%2C%20the%20vehicle%20was%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20dry%2C%26quot%3B%20Cusick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20able%20to%20get%20inside%20and%20start%20his%20truck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20probably%20have%20more%20questions%20than%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Cusick%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20there%20for%20any%20of%20this.%20All%20I%20know%20is%20where%20I%20found%20the%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Rivian%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20A%20Rivian%20spokesperson%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finsideevs.com%2Fnews%2F735934%2Frivian-r1t-flood-hurrican-helene%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInside%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20earlier%20reported%20on%20Cusick's%20truck%2C%20that%20Rivian%20battery%20packs%20are%20sealed%20to%20provide%20floodwater%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20our%20extensive%20battery%20testing%2C%20we%20also%20run%20salt%20spray%20tests%20to%20prove%20that%20our%20corrosion%20mitigations%20through%20the%20life%