ife.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERae%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20storm%20hasn't%20shaken%20her%20love%20for%20Florida.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAllie%20Rae%20is%20a%20mother%2C%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20OnlyFans%20creator%20who%20said%20she%20had%20to%20endure%20Hurricane%20Milton%20with%20her%20family%20in%20their%20high-rise%20condominium%20in%20Clearwater%20Beach%2C%20Florida.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20chronicled%20the%20experience%20on%20TikTok%20as%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40allieraeofficial%2Fvideo%2F7423883364186213675%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etens%20of%20millions%20of%20viewers%20tuned%20in%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20This%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Rae%2C%2040%2C%20and%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20to%20Florida%20about%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20wanting%20to%20get%20away%20from%20the%20Minnesota%20cold.%20We%20wanted%20a%20different%20life%20and%20it's%20beautiful%20down%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20actually%20in%20London%20last%20week%20when%20Milton%20was%20developing%2C%20but%20we%20learned%20how%20serious%20the%20storm%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20day%20we%20flew%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20fly%20straight%20to%20Vegas%20after%20touching%20down%20in%20Florida%20for%20a%20hockey%20game%2C%20but%20our%20tickets%20got%20canceled.%20So%20while%20we%20were%20in%20the%20air%2C%20I%20panic-bought%20five%20tickets%20to%20Houston%20%E2%80%94%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20our%20three%20sons%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20where%20my%20sister%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20hour%20before%20we%20landed%20on%20Monday%2C%20we%20got%20a%20notification%20that%20all%20of%20the%20airports%20were%20shutting%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20never%20our%20intention%20to%20try%20to%20stay%20and%20ride%20out%20the%20storm.%20But%20when%20we%20got%20back%2C%20everyone%20was%20already%20evacuating%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20gas%20or%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20live%20in%20a%20two-story%20penthouse%20in%20Clearwater%20Beach%20in%20a%20mandatory%20evacuation%20zone.%20But%20ultimately%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20our%20best%20bet%20was%20to%20stock%20up%20on%20food%20and%20water%2C%20and%20stay%20in%20the%20high-rise%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a46a97b-9219-4720-b3cb-eaae6d26b961%5C%22%3EIt%20was%20terrifying%20knowing%20there's%20a%20wind%20tunnel%20in%20your%20living%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20things%20started%20picking%20up%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20building%20was%20constructed%20in%20the%20seventies%2C%20and%20our%20unit%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20windows%20%E2%80%94%20only%20about%20half%20of%20which%20were%20shuttered.%20We%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20board%20them%20up%20and%20we%20were%20worried%20they%20would%20shatter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20initial%20plan%20was%20to%20hole%20up%20in%20the%20master%20bedroom.%20Then%20we%20moved%20to%20the%20master%20closet%20and%20eventually%20to%20my%20office%20because%20everything%20was%20shaking%2C%20and%20the%20office%20didn't%20touch%20any%20exterior%20windows%20or%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20windows%20shattered%20on%20the%20main%20floor%2C%20which%20ended%20up%20getting%20flooded%20with%20an%20inch%20or%20two%20of%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20even%20describe%20the%20sounds%20of%20those%20roars.%20It%20was%20terrifying%20knowing%20there%20was%20a%20wind%20tunnel%20in%20your%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20building%20kept%20swaying%2C%20and%20we%20were%20getting%20a%20little%20dizzy%20%E2%80%94%20and%20scared%20it%20might%20collapse.%20We%20even%20packed%20up%20and%20went%20downstairs%20to%20the%20trash%20room%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20building%20temporarily%2C%20but%20ultimately%20decided%20we'd%20be%20safer%20upstairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20scariest%20night%20of%20our%20lives.%20I%20was%20in%20tears%20and%20just%20wanted%20it%20to%20end.%20It%20was%20like%20being%20on%20a%20Ferris%20wheel%20where%20you're%20sick%20and%20want%20to%20get%20off%2C%20but%20it%20just%20won't%20stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d4caab2-7afd-4d42-9297-77d4897bf1df%5C%22%3EThis%20experience%20hasn't%20shaken%20our%20love%20for%20Florida%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20things%20finally%20died%20down%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20we%20all%20took%20our%20air%20mattresses%20to%20the%20master%20bedroom%20and%20went%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaking%20up%20Thursday%20was%20daunting%2C%20but%20there%20are%20parts%20that%20are%20not%20as%20bad%20as%20we%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20windows%20probably%20needed%20to%20be%20replaced%20anyway%2C%20and%20water%20damage%20is%20never%20cheap.%20I'm%20sure%20we%20have%20a%20couple%20hundred%20thousand%20dollars%20worth%20of%20damage%2C%20but%20we%20have%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20plan%20to%20stay%20here%20unless%20we're%20advised%20it's%20not%20safe.%20It's%20a%20large%20condo%20and%20there%20are%20still%20portions%20where%20we%20feel%20safe.%20We%20don't%20have%20power%2C%20but%20there's%20plenty%20of%20water%20and%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20this%20experience%20hasn't%20shaken%20our%20love%20for%20Florida.%20I%20love%20this%20state%2C%20and%20I%20know%20that%20this%20comes%20with%20it.%20And%20I'm%20not%20a%20victim-type%20gal.%20You%20don't%20live%20on%20the%20beach%20and%20have%20paradise%20360%20days%20a%20year%20and%20then%20complain%20when%20this%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20very%20well%20aware%20before%20moving%20here%20that%20these%20storms%20come%20with%20the%20package%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20that.%20You%20become%20better%20at%20preparing%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20live%20out%20in%20the%20suburbs%20of%20Tampa%2C%20but%20I%20choose%20to%20live%20on%20the%20water%20and%20the%20beach.%20I've%20seen%20people%20who%20have%20to%20rebuild%20their%20houses%20constantly.%20For%20now%2C%20I%20take%20the%20emotional%20and%20financial%20risk%20and%20I'm%20comfortable%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-milton-high-rise-condo-mom-family-damage-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728592878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67080f833f2165d716dfed4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-milton-high-rise-condo-mom-family-damage-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIt%20was%20terrifying%20knowing%20there's%20a%20wind%20tunnel%20in%20your%20living%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Clearwater%20Beach%20resident%20Allie%20Rae%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Geoff%20Weiss)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-milton-high-rise-condo-mom-family-damage-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marilyn%20Manson%20Accuser%20Faults%20D.A.%20for%20Waiting%20Two%20Years%20to%20Act%20on%20Rape%20Allegation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1728592314000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FMarilyn-Manson-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236174861%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20%E2%80%9CGame%20of%20Thrones%E2%80%9D%20actor%20who%20has%20accused%20Marilyn%20Manson%20of%20rape%20denounced%20District%20Attorney%20George%20Gasc%C3%B3n%20on%20Thursday%20for%20waiting%20more%20than%20two%20years%20to%20act%20on%20her%20case.%20Esme%20Bianco%20came%20forward%20in%202021%2C%20alleging%20that%20Manson%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Brian%20Warner%20%E2%80%94%20raped%20her%20and%20subjected%20her%20to%20violent%20abuse%2C%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%2