%20doctors%20to%20remove%20the%20ovary%20during%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20most%20cases%2C%20especially%20with%20women%20of%20childbearing%20age%2C%20doctors%20usually%20try%20to%20save%20the%20ovary%2C%20but%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20further%20complications%20and%20more%20surgeries.%20I%20come%20from%20a%20very%20progressive%20family%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20if%20most%20people%20will%20take%20that%20stand.%20I%20know%20of%20friends%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20even%20asked%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20child.%20Doctors%20decided%20for%20them%20and%20saved%20the%20ovary.%20They%20had%20to%20undergo%20another%20surgery%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20Devleena%20shares.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F369525%2Frama-world-mental-health-anxiety-disorder-slow-down-hustle-culture-journalist-breaking-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20agency%20and%20their%20wishes%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren%E2%80%99t%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20she%20rues.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20doctors%20advise%20you%20to%20have%20children%20as%20it%20might%20sort%20out%20some%20issues%20according%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESneha%20also%20chimes%20in.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20just%2025%20and%20not%20married.%20The%20doctor%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20think%20of%20having%20a%20child%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20women%20have%20finally%20found%20solutions%20to%20their%20pain%20after%20years%20of%20struggles.%20Speaking%20to%20many%20other%20women%20in%20the%20same%20boat%2C%20they%20say%20that%20the%20consensus%20remains%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20their%20pain%20is%20not%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20level%20of%20pain%20is%20not%20normal.%20It%E2%80%9