uple%20did%20not%20stop%20there.%20They%20realised%20that%2060%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%20are%20due%20to%20sepsis.%20%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20started%20educating%20village%20health%20workers%20%E2%80%98Aarogya%20Doot%E2%80%99%20(Health%20Messengers)%20to%20detect%20and%20treat%20neonatal%20infections.%20This%20brought%20down%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20to%2020%20per%201%2C000.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducate%20adolescents%20about%20sex%20education%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346145%2Ftermination-of-pregnancy-act-india-dr-nikhil-datar-case-legal-battle-to-raise-abortion-limit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECriminal%20abortions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20highlights%2C%20are%20not%20just%20atrocities%20limited%20to%20tribal%20areas.%20Their%20grip%20extends%20to%20rural%20villages%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CSticks%20and%20local%20herbs%20are%20inserted%20inside%20the%20uterus%20causing%20contractions.%20The%20patient%20is%20forced%20to%20abort%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Rani%20explains.%20Though%20resulting%20in%20the%20desired%20outcome%2C%20the%20sticks%20are%20infective%2C%20causing%20sepsis%20to%20set%20in%20and%20subsequent%20death.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20need%20for%20these%20reductive%20and%20out-of-touch%20procedures%2C%20Dr%20Rani%20highlights.%20%E2%80%9CSince%201971%2C%20India%20has%20legalised%20abortions%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Medical%20Termination%20of%20Pregnancy%20(MTP)%20Act.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fhe