20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F229759%2Fips-hero-lockdown-abuse-call-helpline-raipur-domestic-violence-cases-inspiring-unsung-hero-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereporting%20such%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbika%20too%20was%20suggested%20to%20continue%20to%20endure%20the%20sufferings.%20But%20she%20chose%20to%20leave%20her%20abuser.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20hurt%20me%20more%20was%20that%20society%20still%20supported%20him%20and%20blamed%20me%20for%20leaving%20him.%20My%20neighbours%20suggested%20I%20remain%20quiet%20and%20not%20file%20a%20case%20against%20him%20and%20continue%20to%20endure%20the%20pain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20Chennai-based%20non-profit%2C%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Victim%20Care%2C%20Ambika%20underwent%20surgery%20and%20therapy%20to%20heal%20both%20physically%20and%20emotionally.%20Today%2C%20she%20is%20rebuilding%20her%20life%20and%20works%20as%20a%20welfare%20officer%20with%20the%20same%20organisation.%20As%20a%20single%20parent%2C%20she%20is%20raising%20her%20two%20daughters%20and%20dreams%20of%20a%20country%20where%20they%20are%20safe%20and%20treated%20with%20dignity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20with%20the%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20founder%20Prasanna%20Gettu%20who%20explained%20ways%20to%20create%20safer%20environments%20for%20women%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20ways%20to%20make%20India%20a%20better%20place%20for%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20Prasanna%20went%20to%20Japan%20to%20pursue%20a%20post-doctorate%20diploma%20in%20victimology.%20During%20her%20time%20there%2C%20she%20deepened%20her%20understanding%20of%20victim%20support%20and%20visited%20various%20victim%20assistance%20centres%20across%20the%20country.%20Upon%20returning%20to%20India%2C%20she%20established%20experimental%20victim%20assistance%20centres%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20working%20in%20Japan%2C%20I%20observed%20how%20women%20actively%20sought%20support%20for%20domestic%20violence.%20In%20contrast%2C%20India%20lacks%20adequate%20support%20services%2C%20including%20shelters%2C%20counselling%2C%20and%20legal%20aid%20for%20survivors%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20high%20time%20we%20rethink%20our%20society%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20well-being.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prasanna%20(left)%20founded%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%20Prevention%20and%20Victim%20Care%20to%20assist%20survivors%20of%20domestic%20violence.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fdomestic-violence-4-1728395174-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-369247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrasanna%20(left)%20founded%20the%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Crime%