l%20is%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20seamless%20operations%20at%20his%20%3Cem%3Ekirana%3C%2Fem%3E%20shop%20in%20Hubbali%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20provide%20validation%20to%20former%20banker%20and%20SarvaGram%20co-founder%2C%20Utpal%20Isser.%20He%20explains%20how%20the%20success%20of%20rural%20households%20illustrates%20the%20immense%20potential%20they%20hold.%20The%20inspiration%20to%20start%20a%20business%20that%20focussed%20on%20tipping%20the%20scales%20in%20favour%20of%20such%20homes%2C%20struck%20Utpal%20while%20leading%20the%20rural%20and%20inclusive%20banking%20division%20at%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20largest%20private%20sector%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20provided%20him%20a%20front-row%20seat%20to%20the%20transformation%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20ecosystem%20was%20undergoing%2C%20while%20also%20highlighting%20the%20limitations%20of%20formal%20banking%20institutions%20and%20systems%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20conducive%20to%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWatching%20this%20upward%20mobility%20and%20shift%20in%20infrastructure%20(both%20public%20and%20digital)%20motivated%20us%20to%20look%20for%20a%20business%20model%20that%20would%20take%20care%20of%20the%20realities%20of%20these%20%5Brural%5D%20markets.%20We%20intended%20to%20target%20underbanked%20but%20creditworthy%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20notes.%20Together%20with%20Sameer%20Mishra%2C%20who%20has%20over%2020%20years%20of%20experience%20in%20rural%20finance%2C%20he%20founded%20SarvaGram%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20changed%20many%20lives%20like%20Ishwargowda%E2%80%99s%20with%20access%20to%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5BSarvaGram%5D%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20dream%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20continuing%20success%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utpal%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20rural%20households%20agency%C2%A0%3C%2