mers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20change%20from%20the%20front%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landscape%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20India%20does%20seem%20promising.%20And%20the%20feeling%20continues%20402%20km%20away%2C%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Dreams%20are%20brimming%20at%20the%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%2C%20as%20hundreds%20of%20kids%20who%20study%20at%20the%20school%20share%20their%20aspirations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20get%20into%20sports%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20a%2010-year-old.%20While%20another%20says%20he%20will%20join%20the%20Army.%20Hearing%20these%20innocent%20dreams%20has%20school%20head%20Nandan%20Eshwar%20beaming.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20the%20school%20has%20served%20as%20a%20space%20for%20budding%20talent.%20Nandan%2C%20whose%20uncle%20Channakeshava%20built%20the%20school%2C%20has%20always%20admired%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20persistence%20to%20learn%20and%20dream%20big.%20His%20uncle%2C%20he%20says%2C%20would%20be%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-3-1727934119.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Nisarga%20Vidyanikethana%20High%20School%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20giving%20wings%20to%20childrens'%20professional%20dreams%20and%20aspirations%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-3-1727934119.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-3-1727934119-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-3-1727934119-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%