%20from%20this%2C%20Smita%20shares%20the%20model%20that%20has%20worked%20in%20their%20favour%3B%20one%20that%20involves%20all%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%94%20principals%2C%20teachers%2C%20parents%2C%20and%20students%3B%20thereby%20embedding%20sustainable%20change%20within%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20are%20telling.%20But%20the%20real%20validation%20lies%20in%20heartwarming%20stories%20that%20Smita%20and%20Sumeet%20hear%20every%20now%20and%20then.%20Letting%20us%20in%20on%20one%20such%20anecdote%2C%20Smita%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20teacher%20who%20once%20took%20the%20LEAD%20tab%20in%20her%20hand%20and%20called%20it%20her%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eshikshan%20mitra%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(teacher%E2%80%99s%20friend).%20The%20reason%20for%20calling%20it%20this%2C%20the%20teacher%20went%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20was%20that%20the%20device%20guided%20her%2C%20taught%20her%20what%20to%20do%2C%20and%20gave%20her%20insights%20about%20her%20students.%20It%20was%20everything%20she%20needed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaking%20barriers%20and%20overcoming%20odds%20are%20central%20to%20these%20success%20stories%20you%E2%80%99ve%20just%20read.%20As%20the%20day%20wears%20on%2C%20a%20slight%20drizzle%20announces%20the%20arrival%20of%20dusk.%20Karnataka%20gears%20up%20for%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20heavy%20downpour.%20Shops%20in%20the%20area%20down%20their%20shutters%2C%20and%20Ishwargowda%20Patil%20is%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fenterpreneurship-in-rural-india-6-1727934739.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ishwargowda%20Basavanagowda%20Patil%20has%20a%20thriving%20field%20of%20green%20gram%20that%20he%20cultivates%20once%20he%20has%20wrapped%20up%20his%20kirana%20shop%20operations%20%5C%22%20srcs