%20it%20from%20my%20profile%20when%20it%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20Priya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20confined%20to%20the%20virtual%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20says.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20waste%20my%20life%20on%20perverted%20men%20misusing%20my%20picture%20just%20because%20I%20wore%20a%20skirt.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98To%20talk%20to%20someone%2C%20that%20is%20primary%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20teenagers%20started%20taking%20their%20own%20lives%20over%20video%20games%2C%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20internet%20asserted%20its%20presence.%20Today%2C%20even%20world%20governments%20are%20wary%20of%20its%20influence%20as%20could%20be%20perceived%20from%20reports%20of%20the%202016%20US%20Presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20internet%20can%20be%20a%20more%20dangerous%20world%20than%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20streets%20that%20women%20are%20often%20advised%20to%20avoid%20after%20sunset%E2%80%9D.%20Online%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sunrise%20or%20sunset%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20constant%2C%20deep%2C%20and%20dark%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20have%20stringent%20laws%20yet.%20I%20have%20had%20victims%20showing%20me%20screenshots%20of%20conversations%20where%20the%20perpetrators%20are%20writing%20to%20them%3A%20%E2%80%98Do%20what%20you%20like%2C%20I%20know%20the%20Police%20will%20do%20nothing.%E2%80%99%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20the%20police%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%20anything%3B%20it%20is%20just%20the%20volume%20of%20cases%20and%20the%20anonymity%20that%20online%20media%20allows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20the%20platforms%20are%20also%20not%20very%20prompt%20in%20collaborating%20and%20sharing%20information.%20We%20have%20been%20informed%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20guidelines%2C%20if%20a%20woman%20or%20child%20is%20subjec