n%20countering%20a%20menace%20that%20she%20believes%20is%20a%20pandemic.%20The%20NHRC%20data%20supports%20her%20claims.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20are%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20fallen%20victim%20to%20the%20malicious%20trolls%20that%20make%20the%20internet%20a%20dark%20place%2C%20there%20are%20certain%20steps%20you%20should%20take%2C%20starting%20with%20talking%20to%20someone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20never%20in%20the%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirali%20says%2C%20explaining%20that%20sharing%20an%20incident%20with%20a%20loved%20one%20can%20help%20alleviate%20guilt%20and%20lead%20to%20concrete%20steps%20the%20victim%20can%20take.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20is%20foolproof%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20acknowledges%20but%20asserts%20that%20women%20have%20no%20reason%20to%20feel%20guilty%20or%20ashamed%20because%20of%20a%20pervert%E2%80%99s%20actions%2C%20like%20morphing%20their%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20you%3B%20it%20is%20not%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pritha%20adds.%20As%20time%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20internet%20will%20increasingly%20dictate%20our%20lives%20more%20than%20the%20streets%20do.%20It%E2%80%99s%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20harassment%20is%20harassment%2C%20and%20bullying%20is%20bullying%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20physical%20or%20virtual.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fcyberbullying_11zon-1728365400-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m