f%20experience.%20Recently%2C%20I%20came%20across%20a%20post%20of%20a%20company%20hiring%20project%20engineers%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311587%2Fnashik-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-saffron-in-shipping-container-hyroponics-earn-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20.NET%20developers%20with%20experience%20of%20six%20to%20eight%20years.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20they%20mentioned%20a%20willingness%20to%20accept%20job%20applications%20of%20persons%20with%20a%20gap%20of%20up%20to%20four%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20feedback%20we%20got%20from%20those%20applying%20was%20that%20they%20were%20offered%20a%20salary%20of%20just%20Rs%2025%2C000%20per%20month.%20When%20asked%20why%20the%20applicants%20were%20offered%20such%20a%20low%20salary%2C%20the%20companies%20said%20that%20they%20will%20help%20applicants%20undergo%20training%20for%20three%20months.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20working%20at%20the%20company%2C%20these%20applicants%20will%20qualify%20for%20appraisals.%20Given%20the%20paucity%20of%20opportunities%2C%20many%20end%20up%20accepting%20these%20low-ball%20offers%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20unacceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20is%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20addressing%20this%20pay%20gap%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20the%20ones%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20present%2C%20we%20are%20engaged%20with%20more%20than%20150%20companies%20to%20hire%20more%20women%20in%20their%20workforce.%20Our%20team%20speaks%20to%20these%20companies%2C%20discusses%20their%20salary%20bands%2C%20and%20tells%20them%20what%20the%20industry%20standard%20is%20and%20what%20they%20should%20ideally%20offer.%20If%20the%20companies%20express%20a%20willingness%20to%20interview%20our%20applicants%20and%20discuss%20salary%20offers%20commensurate%20with%20the%20experience%20and%20skill%20set%20of%20our%20applicants%2C%20we%20make%20the%20effort%20to%20help%20them%20diversify%20their%20workforce.%20If%20the%20companies%20are%20hesitant%2C%20we%20step%20back%20and%20ask%20our%20applicants%20not%20to%20compromise%20on%20their%20salary%20demand%20and%20not%20go%20for%20their%20interviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20makes%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20every%20person%20they%20recommend%20to%20companies%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20these%20job%20interviews.%20In%20the%20background%2C%20we%20are%20running%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20applicant%20is%20capable%20enough.%20As%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20we%20connect%20these%20applicants%20to%20mentors%20who%20help%20them%20catch%20up%20to%20the%20latest%20trends%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20and%20fill%20up%20the%20necessary%20gaps%20in%20their%20skill%20sets.%20Moreover%2C%20these%20mentors%20also%20interview%20our%20applicants%20for%20certain%20roles.%20So%2C%20we%20only%20deliver%20these%20interviewed%20people%20to%20the%20companies.%20So%2C%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20person%20(applicant)%20is%20capable%20and%20that%20the%20%5Bjob%5D%20profiles%20are%20filtered%20at%20our%20end%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SheWork%20is%20a%20Pune-based%20company%20dedicated%20to%20hiring%20women%20in%20tech%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWomen-in-Tech-2-1728052657-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%