m%20is%20their%20first%20names%20and%20skill%20sets.%20We%20do%20not%20put%20up%20their%20marital%20status%2C%20surnames%2C%20genders%20(although%20that%E2%80%99s%20sometimes%20difficult%20with%20first%20names)%2C%20etc.%20When%20we%20send%20their%20CVs%2C%20we%20highlight%20their%20skill%20sets%2C%20the%20projects%20they%E2%80%99ve%20worked%20on%2C%20the%20work%20they%20have%20done%2C%20roles%2C%20responsibilities%2C%20etc.%20Once%20they%20are%20selected%20for%20interviews%2C%20we%20communicate%20to%20the%20panels%20at%20these%20companies%20overseeing%20hiring%20to%20record%20them.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20record%20the%20interviews%20so%20that%20our%20candidates%20aren%E2%80%99t%20asked%20questions%20that%20go%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20their%20professional%20capabilities.%20Recording%20these%20interviews%20makes%20recruiters%20conscious%20of%20the%20questions%20they%20ask%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20has%20also%20changed.%20But%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%20%3C%2Fem%3Eapplicants%20are%20only%20looking%20for%20remote%20opportunities%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20telling%20companies%20to%20only%20give%20our%20applicants%20remote%20opportunities.%20The%20current%20trend%20is%20moving%20towards%20hybridisation.%20So%2C%20we%20ask%20companies%20to%20give%20our%20applicants%20hybrid%20work%20opportunities%20but%20with%20some%20flexibility%20as%20well.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20an%20applicant%20just%20had%20a%20baby%20six%20months%20ago%20and%20has%20come%20back%20from%20maternity%20leave%2C%20we%20negotiate%20with%20the%20company%20to%20go%20the%20extra%20mile.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20companies%20have%20a%20five-day%20policy%20of%20coming%20to%20the%20office%2C%20we%20help%20our%20applicant%20negotiate%20for%20three%20days%20because%20she%20has%20a%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pooja.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThankfully%2C%20we%20have%20some%20industry%20leaders%20supporting%20our%20work.%20They%20are%20lending%20us%20a%20helping%20hand%20in%20making%20their%20workplace%20more%20flexible.%20On%20our%20end%2C%20we%20encourage%20our%20applicants%20that%20if%20they%20want%20equal%20pay%20and%20opportunity%2C%20they%20also%20need%20to%20work%20a%20little%20harder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20their%20part%2C%20%3Cem%3ESheWork.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20also%20come%20up%20with%20their%20%3Cem%3EGyno-Care%20Program%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20free%20health%20check%20up%20camps%20for%20women%20IT%20professionals%20in%20association%20with%20partner%20companies%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-7w-8woDPS%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20SheWork%20(%40shework.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3