e%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20for%20female%20foeticides.%20Another%20from%20the%20group%20chips%20in%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20do%20ultrasounds%20to%20peek%20into%20the%20womb.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20%E2%80%98they%E2%80%99%20successful%20in%20these%20killings%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20look%20to%20the%20men%20on%20screen%20for%20answers.%20Statistics%20point%20us%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20a%20skewed%20sex%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201901%2C%20the%20state%20had%20867%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males%20in%20its%20total%20population%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Statistical%20Handbook%20of%20Haryana%202020-21.%20Over%20100%20years%20later%2C%20as%20per%20Census%202011%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20sex%20ratio%20remained%20equally%20worrying%20at%20879%20females%20per%201%2C000%20males.%20These%20are%20proof%20of%20the%20antiquated%20practice%20of%20sex%20determination%20in%20Haryana%2C%20that%20continues%20far%20from%20the%20glare%20of%20modern%20medicine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Filmmaker%20Vibha%20Bakshi%20focuses%20on%20gender%20parity%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20sensitising%20mindsets%20through%20her%20films%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fvibha-bakshi-son-rise-1727705165-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20h